{"tid":510974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警涉藏「K仔」 凌晨突暈倒缺席聆訊","createTime":"2017-12-27T04:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T11:56:44.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"26562eda4b37223092c0afd226aad374f4ae291f","tid":510974,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T04:25:27.000Z","msg":"40歲休班男警去年在街上遭巡邏警員截查，涉嫌在其身上搜出俗稱「K仔」的毒品氯氨酮，他早前否認一項藏毒罪，案件今原於西九龍裁判法院進行審訊，惟辯方指被告今早3時暈倒而到屯門醫院診治，並獲發醫生紙放病假一天，故缺席聆訊。案件將於明年3月14日再訊，控方屆時將傳召3名證人，被告期間獲准以原有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n被告潘俊東報稱警員，被控於去年10月28日在荃灣綠楊新邨平台外，非法管有一個塑料袋，袋內載有1.58克粉末，內含0.38克氯胺酮毒品。"},{"pid":"ef7c6d9282468606a26b12841606b6aa76890c2c","tid":510974,"uid":34444,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T04:29:09.000Z","msg":"香港警察唔單止蠢 仲係好撚蠢添呀"},{"pid":"ccf7e87117edd917cd2081f766a6e523e284f8d1","tid":510974,"uid":152047,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 休班警, 見到呢3隻字就知咩事"},{"pid":"f884a0770e33b140b2961016259c412ccd5c34ac","tid":510974,"uid":86938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:26:53.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人都仲啪野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaf74a89163349256b02fb13d95f07668d4b31f","tid":510974,"uid":90704,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"佢成四十幾歲人 晚晚落去disco 趁<br />\n仲有心臓病 咁high 法遲早都會釘"},{"pid":"4e426e8eaf16f100d4535bf236e3cdee111e9305","tid":510974,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f884a0770e33b140b2961016259c412ccd5c34ac","tid":510974,"uid":86938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:26:53.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人都仲啪野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f87edce93d0625af8e0efb310dd7cb5c86c6c0","ti